metadata.name: Topaz Tribute
metadata.description:
This is the first video that i've made for Aptos NFT ecosystem. This video was the one that got me sucked into this space where amazing people build together on super-fast and seamless chain.

It was the key to get me some exposure and show my art. 

I've included 3 Main projects and then some NFT's from other projects. The last scene is for Topaz Market creator - 0xClickbait

Bruh Bears
Aptomingos
Nevermores

Lecture learnt: Create something for free to get exposure and start your career!
